name: MyWeather
0:
”Alexa, open my weather”
”Alexa, ask my weather for weather at missoula”
”Alexa, ask my weather what is the weather at gulfport mississippi”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my weather
des: My weather is simple skill that provide weather information such as humidity, maximum temperature, minimum temperature, wind speed, sunrise time or sunset time at any place. My weather can give weather info for any day of current week. This skill doesn't required any permissions and user can easily integrate to their Alexa echo or Echo dot devices and use it.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
